where $\Xi = \frac{1}{\sqrt{2 \pi}} \frac{1}{\sqrt{K \lambda}} \frac{m_{H^3}}{\left({m_{H^2}}\right)^\frac32} \frac{\int_0^\infty G^3(t) t dt}{\left({\int_0^\infty G^2(t) t dt}\right)^\frac32}$, and $c(x)$ and $\Psi(x)$ are as given in Theorem \ref{Theorem 1}. 
